<H3>Raw Data - Countries</H3>
Over 75% of the responses received were from the USA, followed by Canada, Australia and the United Kingdom as the countries with the next greatest number of responses.
<P>
<TABLE BORDERCOLOR="#808080" CELLPADDING=2 ALIGN=CENTER BORDER="1">
