<H3>Raw Data - Job Positions</H3>
The positions with the greatest representation in the survey were Maintenance Managers/Superintendents, followed by Plant/Maintenance Engineers, Maintenance Foremen/Supervisors, Maintenance Technicians, and Maintenance Trades/Craftspeople.  There were a higher proportion of all of these job positions in this year's survey compared with last year.
