<H3>Raw Data - Educational Levels</H3>
Educational levels represented were fairly widespread.  It is interesting to note in this years survey the relatively smaller number of trades/crafts trained respondents, but the higher proportion of those with Certificates/Diplomas/Associate Degrees.
